title: Keep it On the Low ( Ashanti Interview)
itunes:title: Keep it On the Low ( Ashanti Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had Ashanti stop by where she spoke about private relationships, re-recording her masters and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Republican Senator Ron Johnson for saying 'standard gargle mouthwash' kills Coronavirus'. Afterwards we opened the phone lines for some good ol' "Slander the Breakfast Club"
